Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your call cannot be connected at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about tonight's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.83,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Ryuuji, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:25.12,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Hey, open your window, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come no matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.17,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are {\i1}you{\i0} do{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that out of the blue?! You're so viole{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Just open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when you open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get ready, so I'll come over in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.45,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)\pos(985.454545,510)}Holy Night Party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god! You look so cute, Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, come over here and check her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you look amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice, it's the perfect size.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it okay for me to borrow these clothes from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not borrowing. They're yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name "R. Aisaka" is sown inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your father's, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just sort of left it because it didn't fit him, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing his castoffs? Are you messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, I'll just throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These sorts of small chores really suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who told me to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Destroy the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say something like that when you can't even say your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Ya-chan will cast some magic on you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now don't go too wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the party starts, this will smell really good mixed in with your scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my father's{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, when I ran away from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a few valuable things with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this is my grandfather's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Stolen goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:47.06,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Write down your name and class when you enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll a catch a cold like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there are a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. There's only one important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you have to do tonight, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yuri-chan-sensei, you dressed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason you're not coming to the party is because you have a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to a course for single women about buying real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Real estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm going to buy an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why today of all days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because women who date on Christmas Eve are far from being prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find something you want, you have to get it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll be leaving now. I need to worry about buying an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, try and stay out of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness the Christmas tree was fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades went up too, so I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd get rewarded for all the effort you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and you too, you'll definitely get what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fantastic single life is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you all for coming out tonight for this party, planned by the God of Broken Hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.07,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We went through a lot of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura's clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.82,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but regardless, this Christmas party is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, we'll lose if you complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I truly appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to have a wonderful time tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to celebrate Christmas Eve, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.51,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Drumsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called turkey, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just normal chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good! As expected of homebred turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, they have cake over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corner over there. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara in hot pants and Nanako-san in an innocent one piece are really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, why is everyone all dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look out of place. I mean, poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on one place while walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor will get sticky if syrup spills on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why I didn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't stand how the drinks were being handled, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm surprised you have such an expensive suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that chicken grease on your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, it's homebred turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.04,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, you're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.29,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Ami-chan yet! She's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I caught a glimpse of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Was she hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she really hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Taiga too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Taiga isn't bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}He's right, where did she go?
