Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about tonight's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.64,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.47,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open your window, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come no matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan and Taiga were both hot, but still cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu! How long are you planning to stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm sure it was different than your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, hot, but still cute and such are basically the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hot, but still cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hot! You're really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn perverted exhibitionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maruo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kihara! Do you think I'm hot, but still cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some fruit punch please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow it turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how was my singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you practice for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't kept a secret, it wouldn't be a surprise, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was totally caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell she tried her best,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to give her some fruit punch as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to Minori-chan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to get Minori to come here and then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something about welcoming Santa, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, maybe there's something she'd rather not see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gave you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think you should stop playing this childish game of house."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why do you have to pretend to be daddy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even listen to me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}In order to give everyone a happy and joyful Christmas,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'm prepared to take off one or two pieces of clothing, or even take it all off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I want to be good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I want to be part of the happy, glittering scene on Christmas Eve...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}while wearing a happy face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, can you get me some fruit punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned too many calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.21,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(700,0)\frz350\fad(500,0)\pos(638,197)}Kushieda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji is waiting for you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he won't leave until he sees you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even prepared to live at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not that you don't like him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Because we're best friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it doesn't work if I'm only good around Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's no Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll be alone this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be alone next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forever. I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never have someone to rely on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one to rely on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa praised my Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,very much, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't take it off, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed it from a guy who was wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what did you do with your suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I traded it with the guy who was wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll definitely get it back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took it off when it was just about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're honestly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I planned everything for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you had the chance to meet Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to believe in Angel Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin is on her way to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you can still make it if you hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already changed my clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't want to leave you by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake Santa and faking being good, it was a fun experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and of course, I'm looking forward to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by some chance things go well with Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow's Christmas meal will be on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken and rice! Beef and rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't have chicken because of Inko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll just be beef and rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up! Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not there at that party, it'll mean I lied to Minorin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa came already, so I have to be good until the end of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just let me be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting Minorin to go to the party is my real Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, indecisive dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to give this back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always relying on Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On his kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those times have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin will definitely fall for Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ryuuji truly likes Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they both like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stay by Ryuuji's side anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to walk by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one beside Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji... Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring my cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my present is still in the pocket of the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great bear, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushie{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but let me speak first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were at A-min's villa during the summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had a talk at night about weird things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about UFOs and ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About UFOs and ghosts, I really think I shouldn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be best to not see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it a lot recently, and this is what I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you that. That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for just saying what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I...
